snippet: The JACK Quartet performed a one-hour program on Governors Island for the Rite of Summer Music Festival, with pieces by composers including Charles Ives and David Crowell.
abstract: Vivien Schweitzer reviews new music performance by the JACK Quartet at Governors Island for the Rite of Summer Music Festival.
lead_paragraph: The JACK Quartet performed a one-hour program on Governors Island for the Rite of Summer Music Festival, with pieces by composers including Charles Ives and David Crowell.
